---
title: HelloHero: Chicken Strips, Bacon & Rainbow Couscous with Dill & Parsley Mayonnaise
description: This bright and flavourful meal features tender chicken thigh in an easy spice blend, with pops of carrot and green leaves stirred through fluffy couscous. Sit back and enjoy this delicious delight with a dollop of herby mayo on top.
